{"tid":344271,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"【狗狗過身】有部近乎全新既移動式冷氣已沒用","createTime":"2017-08-02T07:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T19:42:27.000Z","uid":7980,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43f2dae4ad2574baada3b15ab71dd5216305a89e","tid":344271,"uid":7980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:22:39.000Z","msg":"話說早幾日冷氣壞左,要成個換<br />\n人唔涼狗都要涼...仲要都知佢就去<br />\n盡量想佢舒服D...就托左部冷氣番去吹住佢間房仔<br />\n好唔好彩最後都去左...部機亦無用...<br />\n全新買番黎$5000...7月30先買<br />\n約80CM高50CM闊26CM深<br />\n純粹唔想擺係度等變廢鐵睇下有冇巴絲岩...平讓, 可GOGOVAN送到樓下<br />\n預7折放售...真的跟全新無異<br />\n有興趣TG聯絡, 可再補多D相: <a href=\"https://t.me/TKMRC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTKMRC&d=9V8l8fa56wF2ewEMC3kAMnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=65d7124e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TKMRC</a><br />\n使用簡單...只需隔日倒水箱水及每月洗隔塵網, 兩側吸風/散熱, 上方為冷風出風管<br />\n購買時店方聲稱每小時只需用$0.4電<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/02/152021_d2292616b0cb387570fb337c3cee42c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F02%2F152021_d2292616b0cb387570fb337c3cee42c5.jpg&h=ea9c72a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/02/152023_c4a9360454f40691922bcbe6a3182fb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F02%2F152023_c4a9360454f40691922bcbe6a3182fb6.jpg&h=a6353049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/02/152023_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F02%2F152023_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg&h=17fbd91f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95a81fcaafdbdb636272105db37ad0bfaa19d648","tid":344271,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:38:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d241abf8801c9e630a32e8c1678821